{"tid":683481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳打邊爐真係好平好正呀喂","createTime":"2018-05-29T17:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T02:04:43.000Z","uid":51183,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"db0bd438106d69ee77f2dcd726d292ddda4423d2","tid":683481,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"【觸目驚心火鍋店】<br />\n【火鍋油重用 水杯地拖一齊洗 剩菜回收】<br />\n<br />\n在全國有600百多間加盟店的小龍坎老火鍋，被爆出三間分店有食物安全問題，衛生惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n【吉林長春歐亞店】<br />\n●把客人吃剩的湯底拿回廚房隔出火鍋油，重新提煉，變成紅當當的「口水油」<br />\n●客人投訴肉品有怪味，待應就用豬血蘸一下，「上上色」<br />\n<br />\n【黑龍江哈爾濱會展店】<br />\n●回收客人吃剩的餸菜<br />\n<br />\n【江西南昌店】<br />\n●喝水的杯子與拖把用同一個盆洗，職員表示，「沒有盆，用開水燙一下就好」<br />\n<br />\n小龍坎老火鍋發聲明回應，指涉事的三間分店已停業調查，會加強監管所有分店，又堅持油只可以使用一次，歡迎社會各界參觀廚房。<br />\n<br />\n#小龍坎火鍋<br />\n#口水油<br />\n#好恐怖<br />\n#有同事上星期食過<br />\n#唔好嘔<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1730452040432608/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1730452040432608%2F&d=oJS3i7CeAujLbCyY0Sqywf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1602bda7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1730452040432608/</a><br />\n<br />\n上去打多幾次啦柒頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf781bcae4d71af24d027397310310a2b0eab34","tid":683481,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"po喺飲食台啦<br />\n喺cc台圍爐"},{"pid":"7d941b9b1b21d4cac85347f3a07c4e8a334c9ffe","tid":683481,"uid":112502,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"db0bd438106d69ee77f2dcd726d292ddda4423d2","tid":683481,"uid":51183,"like":0,